                    "line_text": "De la grotte, en lisant, je cherchais le chemin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Du drame de ses jours j'explorais le théâtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
